 calculations and demonstrate that it is possible to combine finite size\nscaling with the finite-element method by using ab initio calculations to\nobtain quantum critical parameters. The combined approach provides a promising\nfirst-principles approach to describe quantum phase transitions for materials\nand extended systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2011 17:09:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2011 17:06:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2012 19:13:43 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 8 Mar 2012 20:49:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-03-16"}
