sical\nparameters (synaptic strength and parameters of calcium dynamics), which are\nknown to be impacted in Parkinson's disease.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2011 18:18:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-09-21"}
