nd more localised for more massive\nstars and for stars with low metallicities further increasing the amplitude of\nthe frequency modulation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2011 20:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
