ions must be associated with\nthe very final phases of stellar evolution, suggestive of some underlying\nnuclear burning instability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2011 20:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
